Tipster
==============

Tipster is a plugin that allows to display contextual tips anywhere in your application.
Those tips are easy to integrate into your views and can be disabled by users.


Example
=======

<% tip "Welcome to Tipster" do %>
    Tipster is a plugin that allows to display contextual tips anywhere in your application.
<% end %>


